title: IGOR CAM STG filtered- easier access, faster download
description: I got this here and cut out most of the bullshit that was there- which was all of the files except the movie-around 60 or so. This is the cam version of IGOR. Quality is ok. Its about what you expect from a cam version. Audio could use better acoustics but its decent and viewable. Great for if your kids want to watch and you can't afford to take them or just choose not to.
